<span id="freeTextContainer16801944009249689427">This is THE BEST Beauty and the Beast story I&apos;ve read. Every other edition that I&apos;ve encountered is too short, too pat, and just doesn&apos;t have the thoroughness and the character-building narrative of this edition.<br/><br/>The psychology of the characters is more complete and convincing. There is a prophetic, mystical challenge for Beauty that is never developed in any other story I&apos;ve seen. Her father and brothers are more tormented and her sisters more conniving.<br/><br/>This is the edition to get and cherish in </span>
