<span id="freeTextContainer17305015731900464504">It&apos;s a lovely rendering of the classic fairy tale! The characters are nicely defined and the story moves along gracefully. I only wish that there were pictures on each page spread. There&apos;s way more prose than picture so I&apos;m not sure it will hold the attention of little ones.<br/><br/>Ages: 7 - 10<br/><br/>Cleanliness: the word &quot;stupid&quot; appears in the story. <br/><br/>**Like my reviews? I also have hundreds of detailed reports that I offer too. These reports give a complete break-down of everything in the book, so you&apos;ll know</span>
