<span id="freeTextContainer16460764655947777017">This is a picture book retelling of the classic Beauty and the Beast story. It was written and illustrated a few years before the animated Disney movie, so adheres to the version in which Beauty has two wicked sisters. <br/><br/>The illustrations are lush and detailed and very romantic. Although intended for children, anyone with an appreciation of Mercer Mayer&apos;s artwork will enjoy this one.</span>
  <span id="freeText16460764655947777017" style="display:none">This is a picture book retelling of the classic Beauty and the Beast story. It was written and illustrated a few years before the animated Disney movie, so adheres to the version in which Beauty has two wicked sisters. <br /><br />The illustrations are lush and detailed and very romantic. Although intended for children, anyone with an appreciation of Mercer Mayer's artwork will enjoy this one.</span>
