<div id="review_2340242911" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2340242911" />
    <a title="Sarajo Mance" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/77145539-sarajo-mance"><img alt="Sarajo Mance" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2340242911?book_show_action=true">Apr 03, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sarajo Mance" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sarajo Mance" href="/user/show/77145539-sarajo-mance">Sarajo Mance</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/77145539-sarajo-mance?shelf=el230">el230</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2340242911" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer389710438766666713">This is a great retelling of the traditional tale. I honestly was not expecting the story to differ from the Disney version of Beauty and the Beast. I personally prefer this version over the Disney version. I believe this will give students the opportunity to explore the origins of different tales.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


