        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3246289666" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16647412229261103117">This book would be an interesting one to read in 2-4th grade because most are familiar with the disney story and I think it would be exciting for the kids to read this book and then compare the disney version to this one. I think the kids could do an assignment to compare the two versions then present it to the class.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


